headline: American Electric Power (AEP) Surpasses Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: AEP (AEP) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +11.72% and +2.92%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
